Structs

Packet.Wrapper

Wrapper which is used to serialize packets in BinaryPack. We cannot serialize Packets directly because

1) We will not know what type to deserialize to and 2) The root object must have a callable constructor so it can't be abstract

This type solves both problems and only adds a single byte to the data.
